Package com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.utility

A set of utility classes used throughout the MinecraftMediaLibrary framework.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArchiveUtilities
    Special archive utilities used throughout the library and also open to users.
    CollectionUtilities
    Special collection utilities used throughout the library and also open to users.
    DebuggerUtilities
    A set of utilities which allow the better debugging output of the media library.
    DependencyUtilities
    Special dependency utilities used throughout the library and also open to users.
    FileUtilities
    Special file utilities used throughout the library and also open to users.
    ImageUtilities
    A series of Image utility functions that are used to extract information about certain image files.
    JavaVersionUtilities
    Class used for determining the version of the Java Runtime Environment and throwing a warning if necessary.
    MinecraftMediaLibraryBuilder
    A builder class which helps users create a MinecraftMediaLibrary instance to use.
    PathUtilities
    A collection of Path utilities useful for determining and extracting information from certain paths.
    ResourcepackUtilities
    Special resourcepack utilities used throughout the library and also open to users.

    RuntimeUtilities

Package com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.utility Description

A set of utility classes used throughout the MinecraftMediaLibrary framework. Feel free to use any of these classes.
